name: ⭕️ THE MLNDRs - S1E1: Down the Neural-Quantum Hole
description: After a long day working at TeraGen® Unlimited, Aaron MLNDR enjoys a healthy dance routine at the CCS58 Metaverse. His available Neural-Quantum® connection credits allow him to enjoy a 6:1 time ratio, thus spending 20 minutes in his favorite environment feels like 2 hours. Isn't that just lovely? He values this time with all of his heart. After all, it is the only activity that helps him disconnect and forget about last month's incident at TeraGen's plant.
